OL,3,CMan paid to dispose of waste is fined
OL,4,Cfor dumping it along dual carriageway
OL,6,FA man from Hampshire has been ordered
OL,7,Fto pay #1,616 in fines and costs for
OL,8,Ffly tipping on a busy dual carriageway.
OL,10,FDalbir Singh from Four Marks pleaded
OL,11,Fguilty at Basingstoke Magistrates
OL,12,FCourt on 17 September 2024 to two
OL,13,Foffences of fly tipping under Section
OL,14,F33 of the Environmental Protection Act
OL,15,F1990.
OL,17,FThe two fly tips were in the laybys
OL,18,Feither side of the A31 near Four Marks.
OL,20,FSingh admitted he had been paid #350
OL,21,Fto take away and dispose of the waste.
